keywhiz.client

Class KeywhizClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • keywhiz.client.KeywhizClient

  • public class KeywhizClient
extends Object
    Client for interacting with the Keywhiz Server. Facilitates the manipulation of Clients, Groups, Secrets and the connections between them.
